    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document gives guidance on securing manually configured IPv6-in- IPv4 tunnels using IPsec in transport mode.  No additional protocol extensions are described beyond those available with the IPsec framework.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
